                     <interp inst="t18190217-104-person961" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live opposite to Mr. Franks. I saw the prisoner lurking about his door - he had no hat on. I watched, saw him take one, and run off. I pursued, and took him with it on his head.</p>
